## Local Development

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.12+
- Node.js 18+
- PostgreSQL (local) or SQLite for dev

### Backend Setup

```bash
cd Backend
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Create a `.env` file:
```env
SECRET_KEY=your-secret-key
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key
DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE=config.settings.development
```

Run migrations and start:
```bash
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
```

### Frontend Setup

```bash
cd Frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

---

## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET/POST | `/application/` | List or create applications |
| GET/DELETE | `/application/{id}/` | Retrieve or delete an application |
| GET/PATCH | `/application/checklist/{id}/` | Update checklist item status or attachment |
| POST | `/application/{id}/chat/` | Ask the AI advisor a question (Pro) |
| GET | `/application/{id}/guide/` | Get AI visa guide |
| GET | `/application/documents/` | List all uploaded documents |
| POST | `/user/register/` | Register a new user |
| GET | `/user/me/` | Get current user profile |
| PATCH | `/user/upgrade/` | Upgrade to Pro |
| GET/POST | `/community/` | List or create questions |
| GET | `/community/{id}/` | Retrieve a question |
| POST | `/community/{id}/comments/` | Add a comment |
| POST | `/api/token/` | Obtain JWT token |
| POST | `/api/token/refresh/` | Refresh JWT token |

---

## Environment Variables

### Backend (Railway)
| Variable | Description |
|---|---|
| `SECRET_KEY` | Django secret key |
| `GEMINI_API_KEY` | Google Gemini API key |
| `DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE` | `config.settings.deployment` |
| `AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID` | AWS IAM user access key |
| `AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY` | AWS IAM user secret key |
| `AWS_DEFAULT_REGION` | `eu-north-1` |

